<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:14:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>跳水——中国选手陈获得女子3米跳板金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-chen-wins-womens-3-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国选手陈怡文周五在巴黎奥运会上夺得女子3米跳板金牌，将中国在2024年奥运会跳水项目上的连胜纪录扩大到七次。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 14:16:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-chen-wins-womens-3-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>由于俄罗斯供应担忧，亚洲液化天然气现货价格维持在 7 个月高位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/asia-spot-lng-prices-remain-7-month-high-amid-russian-supply-concerns-2024-08-09/</link><description>由于担心供应中断，亚洲现货液化天然气（LNG）价格保持在七个多月以来的最高水平，追随欧洲的涨幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 13:44:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/asia-spot-lng-prices-remain-7-month-high-amid-russian-supply-concerns-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人要求投资者加入重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国恒大在周五提交的文件中表示，其清算人已邀请有兴趣重组这家负债累累的房地产开发商或其任何部分的投资者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与越南举行首次海岸警卫队联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五，菲律宾和越南船只的船员用水炮轰击一艘船只，并模拟搜救，这是两国海岸警卫队在南海与北京对峙的首次联合演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部称欧盟电动汽车初裁违反世贸组织规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，欧盟对进口电动汽车（EV）的初步裁决缺乏事实和法律依据，严重违反世界贸易组织（WTO）规则。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>斐济总理将于8月12日至21日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡将于周一至8月21日访问中国，欢迎两国有机会建立战略关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份银行贷款将下降，北京将重点关注政策支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</link><description>路透周五的一项调查显示，尽管央行加大了对经济的政策支持，但受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，中国7月份新增人民币贷款可能较上月大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着国内航空公司向海外扩张，外国航空公司对中国失去了兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</link><description>由于俄罗斯广阔空域飞往欧洲和北美的北方航线较短，中国航空公司享有成本优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:56:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求一些券商对债券交易进行合规检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国证券监管机构已下令一些券商检查其债券交易活动，当局试图遏制对中国政府债券的疯狂购买。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>从百事可乐到宝洁，印度成为下一个增长大赌注，而中国落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pepsico-pg-india-becomes-next-big-growth-bet-china-lags-2024-08-09/</link><description>公司正试图通过推出新的口味和尺寸来满足印度的多样化口味，以吸引其庞大的人口和农村市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pepsico-pg-india-becomes-next-big-growth-bet-china-lags-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份降雨和洪水导致自然灾害损失近一倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</link><description>这是自 2021 年以来 7 月份的最大损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>天气因素导致中国消费价格上涨；国内需求依然疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><description>7月份中国消费者价格上涨速度略快于预期，部分原因是天气因素影响了食品供应，而生产者通货紧缩持续存在，使中国的基本消费趋势保持疲软，这是对政策制定者的考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称交易账户不得借用，中国国债下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</link><description>监管机构对中国炙手可热的债券市场涉嫌不当行为展开调查后，官方媒体表示交易账户不得借用或转让，中国国债周五下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大和澳大利亚瞄准中国，表示加强军事合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</link><description>加拿大和澳大利亚对中国对南海争议海域的主权声索表示震惊，周四表示，两国将加强军事和国防工业合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国因强迫维吾尔人劳动而禁止另外五家中国公司进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</link><description>据政府发布的消息称，美国周四因涉嫌侵犯维吾尔人人权而禁止另外五家中国公司进口产品，这是其从美国供应链中消除强迫劳动制造的商品的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>